statements: SELECT id, app_id, user_id, session_duration, action_type, timestamp FROM app_usage_statistics;
SELECT * FROM app_usage_statistics WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT app_id, user_id, action_type FROM app_usage_statistics ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, session_duration FROM app_usage_statistics WHERE session_duration > 60;
SELECT DISTINCT app_id FROM app_usage_statistics;
SELECT * FROM app_usage_statistics WHERE user_id = 123 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT app_id, COUNT(*) AS total_sessions FROM app_usage_statistics GROUP BY app_id HAVING total_sessions > 10;
SELECT AVG(session_duration) AS average_duration FROM app_usage_statistics WHERE app_id = 456 AND action_type = 'login';
SELECT app_id, COUNT(DISTINCT user_id) AS unique_users FROM app_usage_statistics WHERE action_type LIKE '%search%' GROUP BY app_id;
SELECT app_id, DATE(timestamp) AS date, SUM(session_duration) AS total_duration FROM app_usage_statistics GROUP BY app_id, date ORDER BY date ASC;
SELECT * FROM app_usage
SELECT app_id, user_id, session_id FROM app_usage
SELECT * FROM app_analytics
SELECT app_id, event_type, user_action FROM app_analytics
SELECT event_type, event_time FROM app_analytics
SELECT * FROM app_usage WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY datetime DESC;
SELECT app_id, SUM(duration) AS total_duration FROM app_usage GROUP BY app_id HAVING total_duration > 1000;
SELECT app_id, COUNT(DISTINCT user_id) AS unique_users FROM app_usage GROUP BY app_id;
SELECT app_id, event_type, COUNT(*) AS total_events FROM app_analytics GROUP BY app_id, event_type ORDER BY total_events DESC;
SELECT * FROM app_usage JOIN app_analytics ON app_usage.app_id = app_analytics.app_id WHERE app_usage.user_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM ar_app_sessions;
SELECT app_id, session_start_time, session_end_time FROM ar_app_sessions WHERE session_duration > INTERVAL '1 hour';
SELECT app_id, session_id, session_start_time FROM ar_app_sessions ORDER BY session_start_time DESC;
SELECT event_type, event_timestamp FROM ar_app_events WHERE app_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000' ORDER BY event_timestamp ASC;
SELECT app_id, memory_usage, battery_level FROM ar_app_performance WHERE timestamp >= '2022-07-01' AND timestamp < '2022-08-01';
SELECT * FROM ar_app_sessions ORDER BY session_start_time DESC, session_duration ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT app_id, session_id, user_id FROM ar_app_sessions WHERE session_start_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT app_id, AVG(cpu_usage), MAX(memory_usage) FROM ar_app_performance GROUP BY app_id HAVING AVG(cpu_usage) > 0.5;
SELECT * FROM ar_app_events WHERE event_timestamp >= '2022-06-01' AND event_timestamp <= '2022-06-30' AND event_type IN ('click', 'scroll') ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT app_id, SUM(cpu_usage) AS total_cpu_usage, MIN(memory_usage) AS min_memory_usage FROM ar_app_performance WHERE timestamp >= '2022-07-01' GROUP BY app_id;
SELECT * FROM app_users;
SELECT user_id, username FROM app_users WHERE username='john_doe';
SELECT session_id, session_start, session_end FROM app_sessions ORDER BY session_start DESC;
SELECT event_name, event_timestamp FROM app_events WHERE event_timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY event_timestamp;
SELECT performance_id, cpu_usage, memory_usage FROM app_performance WHERE memory_usage > 80 ORDER BY cpu_usage DESC;
SELECT * FROM app_users WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT user_email FROM app_users WHERE username LIKE 'John%';
SELECT * FROM app_sessions WHERE session_start > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY session_start DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT event_name, event_timestamp FROM app_events WHERE session_id = 10 ORDER BY event_timestamp ASC;
SELECT session_id, AVG(cpu_usage) AS avg_cpu_usage FROM app_performance GROUP BY session_id HAVING avg_cpu_usage > 50;
SELECT * FROM app_users ORDER BY username ASC;
SELECT user_id, username FROM app_users WHERE app_name='MyApp';
SELECT session_id, start_time, end_time FROM app_sessions WHERE duration > 60;
SELECT event_id, event_name, event_time FROM app_events ORDER BY event_time DESC;
SELECT error_id, error_code, error_message FROM app_errors WHERE error_code=404;

SELECT username, app_name FROM app_users WHERE app_name = 'Application A';
SELECT session_id, start_time, end_time, duration FROM app_sessions WHERE user_id = 10 ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT event_name, event_time FROM app_events WHERE session_id = 5 AND event_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01';
SELECT error_code, error_message FROM app_errors WHERE session_id = 3 AND error_code >= 500 ORDER BY error_code ASC;
